data.description: A RARE PROPERTY! MORENO VALLEY PROPERTY ON A CORNER LOT, a quiet location with an empty space to the right, near neighborhood shopping centers and schools. It has 2 car garage but can add extra room, and has concrete frontage that can park 3 more cars. It has a great landscape with exotic flowers you can really appreciate. It has fantastic floor plan, all upgraded with high ceiling and a spacious living area with fireplace and a corner sink, and a wall opening to the spacious kitchen and also to the family. A spacious family room with sliding door to the beautiful garden with lots of fruit trees you will enjoy. Owner spent thousands for upgrades and also to plant and care for abundance of fruit trees his family can enjoy. Bathrooms has upgraded glass showers. Master suite with walk-in closet and a spacious bathroom with glass shower. It is adjacent to another room that is very practical as nursery to family with newborn baby. It has a central air-conditioning located in the attic, and brand-new ceiling fans. You will surely enjoy this property as your family home!
